{"tid":911544,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"[痴撚線]曼城接近以90m收購阿積士防中Frenkie de Jong","createTime":"2018-11-22T03:54:05.000Z","updateTime":"2018-11-22T18:33:27.000Z","uid":5649,"like":4,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"ba7858c067e517de0bd10c0dd94003945b6f7506","tid":911544,"uid":5649,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-22T03:54:05.000Z","msg":"Sam Lee: Manchester City close in on Frenkie de Jong with Barcelona set to give up<br />\r\n<br />\r\nCity have informed Ajax of their willingness to pay &euro;70 million (&pound;62 million) with a further &euro;20 million (&pound;18 million) in bonuses for De Jong, making it a potential &euro;90 million (&pound;80 million) deal.<br />\r\n<br />\r\nCity believe they are very well-placed to sign De Jong after months of talks between sporting director Txiki Begiristain and Marc Overmars, who holds the same position at the Dutch giants.<br />\r\n<br />\r\n<strong><em>Wary of past deals that seemed done then went wrong, such as Alexis Sanchez, Dani Alves and Jorginho,</em></strong> City are working hard to make sure the same doesn&rsquo;t happen with De Jong, and a deal could even be completed in the coming months, with the player then loaned back to Ajax until the summer.<br />\r\n<br />\r<br />\r\n<a href=\"https://www.mcfcwatch.com/2018/11/21/sam-lee-manchester-city-close-in-on-frenkie-de-jong-with-barcelona-to-give-up/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.mcfcwatch.com%2F2018%2F11%2F21%2Fsam-lee-manchester-city-close-in-on-frenkie-de-jong-with-barcelona-to-give-up%2F&d=zRU%2FTC47Z3kq%2BDheERVB1J7TfgnX9jywtYe9GXZmhCU%3D&h=89e9584a\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.mcfcwatch.com/2018/11/21/sam-lee-manchester-city-close-in-on-frenkie-de-jong-with-barcelona-to-give-up/</a>"},{"pid":"ef81c6da4bdbc827736285c3a3822f3f8c97bc63","tid":911544,"uid":221419,"like":3,"dislike":4,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-22T03:55:26.000Z","msg":"Inb4 49000 入來屌金錢足球<img src=\"/asset